<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">Carlos A. Salvagni , vice president , pharmaceutical manufacturing ,</COREF> will assume responsibility for manufacturing in Kalamazoo , Mich. , effective Nov. 1 .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Salvagni , 53 years old ,</COREF> succeeds John C. Griffin , 57 , who is retiring as corporate vice president of pharmaceutical manufacturing .
Upjohn is a world - wide provider of health - care products and services , seeds and speciality chemicals .
